20been%20purely%20Gambhir's%20choice%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHarshit%20Rana%20has%20been%20completely%20Gautam%20Gambhir's%20choice.%20He%20has%20been%20pushing%20his%20case%20for%20the%20longest%20time%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Sri%20Lanka%20tour%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0a%20BCCI%20source%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20bowls%20consistently%20in%20the%20140-click%20range%20and%20has%20a%20good%20short%20ball%20apart%20from%20being%20able%20to%20nail%20his%20yorkers%20perfectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20also%20kept%20as%20a%20reserve%20bowler.%20Since%20he%20is%20younger%20and%20quicker%20than%20both%20Navdeep%20Saini%20and%20Mukesh%20Kumar%2C%20he%20has%20pipped%20them%20to%20the%20final%20squad%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20pacer%20Mohammed%20Shami%20is%20not%20part%20of%20the%20squad%20while%20left-arm%20wrist%20spinner%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20has%20been%20advised%20long-term%20rehabilitation%20for%20his%20groin%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20squad%20that%20was%20picked%20for%20the%20New%20Zealand%20series%2C%20Axar%20Patel%20has%20been%20dropped%20as%20off-spinner%20Washington%20Sundar%2C%20who%20has%2011%20wickets%20in%20his%20kitty%20so%20far%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Test%20in%20Pune%2C%20preferred%20over%20the%20Gujarat%20left-arm%20spinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20man%20Abhimanyu%20Easwaran%20has%20entered%20the%20squad%20as%20reserve%20opener%20after%20four%20back-to-back%20hundreds%20in%20Duleep%2C%20Irani%20and%20Ranji%20Trophy%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cover%20is%20because%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20Rohit%20skipping%20one%20of%20the%20earlier%20Test%20matches%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKL%20Rahul%20and%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20make%20up%20for%20the%20middle-order%20with%20Rishabh%20Pant%20and%20Dhruv%20Jurel%20being%20the%20two%20wicket-keepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasidh%20Krishna%2C%20the%20lanky%20pacer%20who%20made%20his%20debut%20in%20South%20Africa%20last%20year%2C%20is%20back%20in%20the%20squad%20after%20a%20long%20injury%20lay-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20Nitish%20Reddy%20is%20concerned%2C%20he%20has%20one%20century%20and%20two%20five-wicket%20hauls%20in%20his%2021%20First-Class%20games%20and%20he%20was%20more%20of%20a%20forced%20choice%20as%20the%20seam%20bowling%20all-rounder%20cupboard%20is%20bare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHardik%20Pandya%20has%20stopped%20playing%20red-ball%20cricket%20and%20Shivam%20Dube's%20(he%20is%20injured)%20bowling%20isn't%20up%20to%20the%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNitish%20is%20a%20work%20in%20progress%20but%20if%20India%20are%20to%20bring%20in%20balance%2C%20they%20need%20their%20fourth%20seamer%20to%20be%20an%20all-rounder.%20Hence%20Nitish%20is%20a%20desperate%20choice%20going%20by%20his%20IPL%20and%20Bangladesh%20series%20performance%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20understood%20that%20it%20won't%20be%20surprising%20if%20Washington%20gets%20ahead%20in%20pecking%20order%20in%20Australia%20for%20the%20second%20spinner's%20slot%20(first%20spinner%20would%20be%20Ravindra%20Jadeja)%20over%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20due%20to%20his%20superior%20batting%20skills%20which%20has%20already%20been%20tested%20in%20Australia%20during%20the%20last%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20batsmen%2C%20Easwaran%20was%20rewarded%20for%20his%20four%20hundreds%20on%20the%20trot%20but%20he%20could%20also%20be%20a%20stonewaller%20like%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara%20if%20needed%20be%20during%20any%20part%20of%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxar%20had%20to%20miss%20out%20because%20he%20would%20have%20been%20one%20spinner%20too%20many%20with%20Jadeja%20already%20in%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayank%20Yadav%20injured%20again%20%2C%20India's%20fastest%20bowler%20Mayank%20Yadav%20is%20injured%20again%20after%20an%20impressive%20international%20debut%20against%20Bangladesh%20as%20he%20missed%20out%2