teenager%20and%20built%20what%20can%20only%20be%20described%20as%20a%20paedophile%20enterprise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20outside%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMcCartney%20is%20a%20dangerous%2C%20relentless%2C%20cruel%20paedophile%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECimarron%20Thomas%20from%20West%20Virginia%20in%20the%20United%20States%20took%20her%20own%20life%20in%20May%202018%20after%20McCartney%20demanded%20that%20she%20involve%20her%20younger%20sister%20in%20sex%20acts%20he%20had%20coerced%20her%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEighteen%20months%20later%2C%20her%20distraught%20father%20Ben%20Thomas%20also%20died%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelfast%20Crown%20Court%20heard%20earlier%20other%20victims%20had%20been%20in%20the%20United%20States%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Sexual%20deviant'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESentencing%20McCartney%2C%20judge%20John%20O'Hara%20said%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20any%20other%20case%20in%20which%20an%20offender%20had%20used%20social%20media%20to%20%26quot%3Binflict%20such%20terrible%20and%20catastrophic%20damage%20on%20young%20girls%20up%20to%20and%20including%20the%20death%20of%20a%2012-year-old%20girl%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20truly%20difficult%20to%20think%20of%20a%20sexual%20deviant%20who%20poses%20a%20greater%20risk%20than%20this%20defendant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO'Hara%20said%20McCartney%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bremorseless%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20offending%2C%20ignoring%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20pleas%20for%20mercy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20his%20third%20arrest%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20former%20computer%20science%20student%20kept%20offending%20in%20%26quot%3Ban%20even%20more%20sinister%2C%20dramatic%20and%20appalling%20manner%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcCartney%20previously%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20manslaughter%20relating%20to%20Cimarron's%