-iran-6875837%5C%22%3E%20Israeli%20officials%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20clarified%20that%20these%20attacks%20are%20justified%20as%20measures%20of%20self-defence.%20IDF's%20spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%20also%20urged%20Israeli%20citizens%20to%20%26quot%3Bremain%20alert%20and%20vigilant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20United%20States%20confirmed%20it%20was%20informed%20of%20the%20impending%20strike%2C%20although%20no%20US%20personnel%20or%20assets%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20operation.%20Sean%20Savett%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20White%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%2C%20termed%20Israel's%20actions%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20exercise%20of%20self-defence%20and%20in%20response%20to%20Iran's%20ballistic%20missile%20attack%20against%20Israel.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIranian%20state%20TV%20reported%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20explosions%26quot%3B%20around%20Tehran%20on%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20without%20specifying%20their%20cause.%20The%20semi-official%20Tasnim%20News%20Agency%20noted%20that%20no%20rockets%20or%20aircraft%20were%20reported%20in%20the%20skies%20over%20Tehran%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20explosions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIranian%20state%20TV%20claimed%20that%20the%20blasts%20heard%20around%20Tehran%20were%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bactivation%20of%20the%20air%20defence%20system.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20loud%20blasts%20heard%20around%20Tehran%20were%20related%20to%20the%20activation%20of%20the%20air%20defence%20system%20against%20the%20actions%20of%20Zionist%20regime%20which%20attacked%20three%20locations%20outside%20of%20Tehran%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20state%20TV%20reported%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIranian%20authorities%20suggested%20the%20noises%20could%20be%20related%20to%20defensive%20measures%2C%20hinting%20at%20the%20possibility%20that%20Iran's%20air%20defence%20systems%20had%20been%20activated.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Tehran%2C%20residents%20in%20the%20nearby%20city%20of%20Karaj%20reported%20hearing%20blasts.%20Iranian%20authorities%20say%20that%20operations%20at%20critical%20sites%20such%20as%20the%20Imam%20Khomeini%20International%20Airport%2C%20Mehrabad%20Airport%2C%20and%20a%20prominent%20oil%20refinery%20south%20of%20Tehran%20were%20%26quot%3Bnormal%26quot%3B%20and%20unaffected%20by%20the%20strikes.%20However%2C%20several%20military%20bases%20near%20Tehran%20were%20reportedly%20targeted%20by%20Israeli%20forces%2C%20according%20to%20Iran's%20Fars%20News%20Agency.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReports%20of%20explosions%20from%20Syria's%20state%20news%20agency%20SANA%20noted%20that%20Syrian%20air%20defences%20were%20activated%20in%20response%20to%20%26quot%3Bhostile%20targets%26quot%3B%20near%20the%20capital%2C%20Damascus.%20While%20there%20was%20no%20official%20statement%20connecting%20the%20Syrian%20incidents%20directly%20to%20the%20Israeli%20strikes%20in%20Iran%2C%20explosions%20were%20heard%20in%20Damascus%20and%20central%20regions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20Israel%20has%20intensified%20operations%20against%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20-%20both%20allies%20of%20Iran%20-%20following%20an%20unprecedented%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20brutal%20assault%2C%20labelled%20the%20deadliest%20attack%20in%20Israel's%20history%2C%20has%20triggered%20relentless%20Israeli%20offensives%20across%20Gaza%20and%20heightened%20security%20measures%20along%20Israel's%20northern%20border%20with%20Lebanon%20to%20counter%20Hezbollah's%20influence.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIsrael's%20defence%20minister%20warned%20earlier%20this%20week%20that%20any%20attempt%20to%20harm%20Israel%20would%20result%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bheavy%20price%26quot%3B.%20The%20United%20States%2C%20while%20voicing%20its%20support%20for%20Israel's%20right%20to%20defend%20itself%2C%20has%20been%20diplomatically%20active%2C%20pushing%20to%20prevent%20a%20chain%20reaction%20that%20could%20destabilise%20the%20entire%20region.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729907220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2lceiu2_netanyahu-khamenei-_625x300_04_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-war-israel-conducts-precise-strikes-on-iran-explosions-heard-around-tehran-6876065%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20has%20launched%20targeted%20strikes%20against%20Iran%2C%20with%20its%20military%20saying%20the%20strikes%20are%20in%20response%20to%20the%20October%201%20missile%20attack%2C%20during%20which%20Iran%20fired%20approximately%20200%20ballistic%20missiles%20at%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-war-israel-conducts-precise-strikes-on-iran-explosions-heard-around-tehran-6876065%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inflation%20moderating%2C%20upside%20risks%20require%20vigilance%3A%20RBI%20Guv%20Das%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729905901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Finflation-moderating-upside-risks-require-vigilance-rbi-guv-das-124102600031_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20economy%20is%20expanding%20at%20a%20solid%20clip%20with%20the%20balance%20of%20growth%20and%20inflation%20well-poised%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Finflation-moderating-upside-risks-require-vigilance-rbi-guv-das-124102600031_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Green%20camo%20%26amp%3B%20combat%20boots%20on%2C%20Indonesia's%20new%20president%20trains%20his%20cabinet%20at%20military%20camp%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729905673000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fpho