y%20believe%20are%20fueling%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEmarketer%20analyst%20Jacob%20Bourne%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bsurprise%20element%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20biggest%20contributor.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20stock%20price%20has%20been%20on%20a%20tear%20in%20the%20two%20days%20since%20the%20carmaker%20reported%20quarterly%20earnings%20that%20exceeded%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20regained%20the%20ground%20it%20lost%20following%20Tesla's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-robotaxi-event-cybercab-elon-musk-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWe%2C%20Robot%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20event%20on%20October%2010%2C%20during%20which%20Elon%20Musk%20showed%20off%20the%20Cybercab.%20He%20was%20lighter%20on%20launch%20specifics%20than%20some%20on%20Wall%20Street%20wanted%2C%20and%20the%20stock%20fell%209%25%20the%20following%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20later%2C%20Tesla%20closed%20the%20week%20with%20a%20share%20price%20of%20%24269.19%20on%20Friday%20%E2%80%94%20its%20highest%20since%20September%202023.%20The%20stock%20is%20now%20up%208.33%25%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvaTrade's%20chief%20market%20analyst%2C%20Kate%20Leaman%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20Tesla's%20earnings%20were%20a%20%26quot%3Bsurprise%20beat%2C%20which%20always%20gives%20the%20stock%20a%20push.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20announced%20better-than-expected%20profit%20and%20gross%20margin%2C%20a%20closely%20watched%20number.%20It%20also%20announced%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-profit-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECybertruck%20hit%20profitability%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20it%20was%20on%20track%20to%20start%20production%20for%20more%20affordable%20EVs%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacob%20Bourne%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Emarketer%2C%20a%20sister%20company%20to%20