20Standard%20on%20its%20%26quot%3BBrave%20New%20World%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20most%20wonderful%20thing%2C%20my%20little%20blue%20spot%20walking%20down%20the%20street%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20the%20technology.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20find%20it%20completely%20magical%20and%20unbelievable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMirren's%20comments%20went%20viral%20online%20after%20other%20publications%20aggregated%20them%20from%20The%20Standard.%20On%20social%20media%2C%20people%20compared%20the%20quotation%20to%20the%20satire%20website%20Clickhole%2C%20which%20regularly%20posts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FClickHole%2Fstatus%2F1849194089817747627%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimages%20of%20celebrities%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20fabricated%20quotes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20of%20Cobain's%20death%20does%20functionally%20illustrate%20Mirren's%20point%2C%20even%20though%20it's%20a%20roundabout%20way%20to%20get%20there%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-internet-and-how-the-internet-works2011-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20first%20webpage%3C%2Fa%3E%20went%20live%20in%201991%2C%20and%20the%20Mosaic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2010%2F04%2F0422mosaic-web-browser%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweb%20browser%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20released%20in%201993%20and%20could%20simultaneously%20display%20photos%20and%20text%2C%20made%20the%20internet%20more%20accessible%20to%20the%20general%20public.%20It%20wasn't%20until%202007%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2007%2F12%2F26%2F17611103%2Fgps-goes-mainsteam%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENPR%3C%2Fa%3E%20declared%20that%20GPS%20had%20gone%20%26quot%3Bmainstream%26quot%3B%20through%20personal%20devices%2C%20the%20same%20year%20that%20Google%20Maps%20launched%20on%20smartphones.%20Five%20years%20later%2C%20Apple%20launched%20its%20own%20smartphone-based%20product%2C%20Apple%20Maps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20Kurt%20Cobain%20did%20not%20experience%20the%20GPS%20experience%20that%20Mirren%20describes.%20But%20she's%20right%20about%20something%20else%3A%20she%20does%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3Balways%26quot%3B%20bring%20up%20Cobain%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20actor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oprah.com%2Fspirit%2Fdame-helen-mirren-the-100-foot-journey%2Fall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esat%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Oprah%20Winfrey%20for%20her%20film%20%26quot%3BThe%20100%20Foot%20Journey.%26quot%3B%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Winfrey%20remarked%20on%20Mirren's%20%26quot%3Benergy%20and%20vibrancy%26quot%3B%20despite%20her%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20either%20die%20young%20or%20get%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20Mirren%20said%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20other%20way.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20die%20young.%20Look%20at%20Kurt%20Cobain%20%E2%80%94%20he%20hardly%20even%20saw%20a%20computer!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com%2Fuk%2Fbeauty-hair%2Fcelebrity-hair-makeup%2Fa37559%2Fdame-helen-mirren-loreal-paris-interview%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECosmopolitan%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bthinking%20about%20Kurt%20Cobain%20the%20other%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20she%20was%20stunned%20that%20he%20had%20never%20experienced%20the%20internet.%20She%20made%20similar%20remarks%20to%20beauty%20publication%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.getthegloss.com%2Fbeauty%2Fhair%2Fan-audience-with-the-queen-helen-mirren-on-age-beauty-and-l-or-al%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGet%20the%20Gloss%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20same%20year%2C%20and%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Ftvshowbiz%2Farticle-3400373%2FMy-life-s-litany-mistakes-reveals-Dame-Helen-Mirren-wouldn-t-want-way.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Daily%20Mail%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E