%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Washington%20Post%20CEO%20Will%20Lewis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671bfae99b3250dbbcea598b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWashington%20Post%20CEO%20Will%20Lewis%2C%20seen%20in%202017%2C%20announced%20the%20newspaper's%20decision%20not%20to%20announce%20a%20candidate%20this%20year.%3Cp%3EDia%20Dipasupil%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20cowardice%2C%20with%20democracy%20as%20its%20casualty%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marty%20Baron%2C%20who%20was%20the%20Post's%20top%20editor%20from%202012%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F2021.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E2021%2C%20in%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FPostBaron%2Fstatus%2F1849847940761657353%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETwitter%2FX%20post%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3B%40realdonaldtrump%20will%20see%20this%20as%20an%20invitation%20to%20further%20intimidate%20owner%20%40jeffbezos%20(and%20others).%20Disturbing%20spinelessness%20at%20an%20institution%20famed%20for%20courage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2F2024%2F10%2F25%2Fwashington-post-endorsement%2F%3Futm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demail%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWill%20Lewis%2C%20the%20Post's%20publisher%20and%20CEO%2C%20announced%20the%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20to%20endorse%20in%20a%20bylined%20announcement%2C%20framing%20it%20as%20a%20return%20to%20the%20paper's%20history.%20Though%20the%20paper%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2Fhillary-clinton-for-president%2F2016%2F10%2F12%2F665f9698-8caf-11e6-bf8a-3d26847eeed4_story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendorsed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2F2020%2F09%2F28%2Feditorial-board-endorsement-joe-biden%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopponents%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20previous%20two%20presidential%20elections%2C%20prior%20to%20the%201976%20election%2C%20the%20Post%20didn't%20make%20presidential%20endorsements%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20it%20right%20before%20that%2C%20and%20this%20is%20what%20we%20are%20going%20back%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20Post%20story%2C%20though%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fstyle%2Fmedia%2F2024%2F10%2F25%2Fwashington-post-endorsement-president%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereports%20that%20the%20Post's%20editorial%20page%20had%20already%20drafted%20a%20Kamala%20Harris%20endorsement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20cites%20unnamed%20sources%20who%20say%20Bezos%20made%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20run%20the%20endorsement.%20In%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%2C%20Post%20Chief%20Communications%20Officer%20Kathy%20Baird%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20Washington%20Post%20decision%20to%20not%20endorse%2C%20and%20I%20would%20refer%20you%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2F2024%2F10%2F25%2Fwashington-post-endorsement%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublisher's%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20full.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22782b6043-c5e3-4e24-a027-093887304920%5C%22%3EExplaining%20the%20non-endorsement%20decision%20in%20LA%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%2C%20owner%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdrpatsoonshiong%2Fstatus%2F1849217132183060705%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESoon-Shiong%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20on%20Twitter%2FX%20on%20Wednesday%20trying%20to%20explain%20the%20paper's%20non-endorsement.%20Instead%20of%20an%20endorsement%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20had%20told%20his%20editorial%20board%20to%20draft%20a%20%26quot%3Bfactual%20analysis%20of%20all%20the%20%5Bsic%5D%20POSITIVE%20AND%20NEGATIVE%20policies%20by%20EACH%20candidate%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20that%20%26quot%3Bour%20readers%20could%20decide%20who%20would%20be%20worthy%20of%20being%20President.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20adopting%20this%20path%20as%20suggested%2C%20the%20Editorial%20Board%20chose%20to%20remain%20silent%20and%20I%20accepted%20their%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20bit%20hard%20to%20understand%20how%20Soon-Shiong%20thought%20this%20would%20work.%20Earlier%20this%20summer%2C%20the%20Times'%20editorial%20board%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fopinion%2Fstory%2F2024-07-11%2Fla-trump-unfit-for-office-biden-election%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealready%20declared%20that%20Trump%20was%20%26quot%3Bpatently%20unfit%20for%20office%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ban%20imminent%20threat%20to%20democracy.%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20If%20you're%20starting%20from%20that%20point%2C%20a%20pros%20and%20cons%20list%20doesn't%20seem%20particularly%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20Mariel%20Garza%2C%20the%20editorials%20editor%20of%20the%20LA%20Times%2C%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cjr.org%2Fbusiness_of_news%2Flos-angeles-times-editorials-editor-resigns-after-owner-blocks-presidential-endorsement.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EColumbia%20Journalism%20Review%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20hadn't%20gotten%20a%20request%20like%20that%20from%20Soon-Shiong.%20She%20resigned%20in%20protest%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%20it%20matters%20that%20the%20largest%20newspaper%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20nation%20still%20%E2%80%94%20declined%20to%20endorse%20in%20a%20race%20this%20important.%20And%20it%20matters%20that%20we%20won't%20even%20be%20straight%20with%20people%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20her%20resignation%20letter.%20%26quot%3BThe%20non-endorsement%20undermines%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20editorial%20board%20and%20every%20single%20endorsement%20we%20make%2C%20down%20to%20school%20board%20races.%20People%20will%20justifiably%20wonder%20if%20each%20endorsement%20was%20a%20decision%20made%20by%20a%20group%20of%20journalists%20after%20extensive%20research%20and%20discussion%2C%20or%20through%20decree%20by%20the%20owner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20next%20day%2C%20Soon-Shiong's%20daughter%20Nika%2C%20an%20outspoken%20opponent%20of%20Israel's%20military%20action%20in%20Gaza%2C%20complicated%20matters%20with%20her%20own%20series%20of%20Twitter%20posts%2C%20which%20seemed%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20paper's%20non-endorsement%20was%20a%20reaction%20to%20that%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20controversy%20and%20confusion%20over%20the%20LAT%E2%80%99s%20decision%20not%20to%20endorse%20a%20presidential%20candidate.%20I%20trust%20the%20Editorial%20Board%E2%80%99s%20judgment.%20For%20me%2C%20genocide%20is%20the%20line%20in%20the%20sand.%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Nika%20Soon-Shiong%20%F0%9F%87%B5%F0%9F%87%B8%20(%40nikasoonshiong)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnikasoonshiong%2Fstatus%2F1849671252052439145%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20asked%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20for%20comment%20or%20clarification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20back%20to%20where%20we%20started%3A%20There's%20little%20debate%20about%20whether%20people%20who%20own%20newspapers%20can%20influence%20what%20those%20newspapers%20publish.%20(Whether%20they%20%3Cem%3Eshould%