20and%20allergies%20may%20have%20difficulty%20finding%20the%20best%20dog%20subscription%20box%2C%20as%20many%20services%20don't%20offer%20this%20level%20of%20customization.%20That's%20where%20Pooch%20Perks%20comes%20in.%20This%20box%20provides%20an%20impressive%20array%20of%20customization%20options%3A%20You%20can%20choose%20durable%20or%20plush%20toys%20for%20your%20pup's%20box%20and%20request%20specific%20ingredients%20be%20included%20or%20excluded%20from%20treats.%20The%20boxes%20are%20tailored%20to%20your%20dog's%20size%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20prepaid%20subscription%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20receiving%20our%20Pooch%20Box%2C%20we%20immediately%20liked%20the%20included%20treats.%20The%20brand%20does%20a%20great%20job%20of%20sourcing%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-treats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20treats%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20your%20pup%2C%20and%20our%20test%20dog%20loved%20the%20beef%20jerky%20chews%2C%20biscuits%2C%20and%20specialty%20chicken%20jerky%20chew%20tucked%20in%20the%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20the%20plush%20toys%20box%2C%20and%20while%20they%20were%20popular%20with%20our%20dog%2C%20they%20weren't%20the%20best%20we've%20seen.%20They%20were%20easy%20to%20damage%20when%20we%20simulated%20lighter%20play%20before%20handing%20them%20over%20to%20our%20super%20chewer.%20A%20few%20threads%20popped%20out%20of%20one%20of%20the%20toys%20when%20we%20scratched%20it%20with%20a%20dinner%20fork.%20However%2C%20the%20brand%20does%20offer%20a%20durable%20toy%20box%20for%20more%20aggressive%20pups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20dog%20subscription%20boxes%3Cp%3EBefore%20buying%20a%20dog%20subscription%20box%2C%20consider%20a%20few%20factors.%20Most%20boxes%20include%20toys%20and%20treats%2C%20but%20some%20are%20specifically%20designed%20for%20small%20or%20large%20breeds%20and%20may%20not%20be%20suitable%20for%20every%20pup.%20The%20experts%20we%20consulted%20also%20provided%20some%20advice%20on%20what%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20box%20for%20your%20dog.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETreats%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Treats%20shouldn't%20make%20up%20more%20than%2010%25%20of%20your%20dog's%20diet%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.carolstreamah.com%2Fmeet-our-team.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Mondrian%20Contreras%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20veterinarian%20and%20owner%20of%20Carol%20Stream%20Animal%20Hospital.%20We%20recommend%20slowly%20integrating%20subscription%20box%20treats%20into%20your%20dog's%20diet%20to%20ensure%20they%20don't%20have%20any%20adverse%20reactions%2C%20like%20an%20upset%20stomach.%20We%20also%20recommend%20treats%20with%20the%20ingredients%20and%20nutritional%20information%20printed%20on%20the%20label%20so%20you%20know%20exactly%20what%20you're%20feeding%20your%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EToys%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Ferinleighaskeland%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EErin%20Askeland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20professional%20dog%20trainer%20and%20animal%20health%20and%20behavioral%20expert%20for%20Camp%20Bow%20Wow%2C%20says%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-toy%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20toys%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20differ%20for%20each%20pup%2C%20but%20generally%2C%20sturdier%20toys%20are%20better.%20She%20also%20prefers%20toys%20that%20lack%20additional%20parts%2C%20such%20as%20small%20sewn-on%20buttons%20and%20googly%20eyes%20that%20are%20easy%20to%20swallow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20also%20advise%20against%20toys%20you%20can't%20indent%20with%20a%20fingernail%2C%20as%20they%20can%20damage%20a%20dog's%20teeth.%20For%20super%20chewers%2C%20durable%20rubber%20is%20a%20good%20option%20that%20can%20often%20withstand%20strong%20jaws%2C%20but%20smaller%20pups%20will%20have%20more%20trouble%20with%20these%20heavy-duty%20toys.%20Ideally%2C%20the%20best%20dog%20subscription%20boxes%20provide%20options%20for%20pups%20big%20and%20small%2C%20with%20appropriate%20toys%20for%20their%20size%20and%20chewing%20ability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndividual%20preferences%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20best%20dog%20subscription%20box%20is%20the%20one%20that%20suits%20your%20pup's%20needs%20and%20preferences.%20Toys%2C%20especially%2C%20can%20be%20challenging%20to%20select.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20there's%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20trial%20and%20error%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Askeland.%20We%20recommend%20starting%20with%20a%20one-time%20box%20purchase%20before%20committing%20to%20a%20subscription.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20dog%20subscription%20boxes%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20pitbull%20mix%20is%20playing%20tug%20with%20a%20yellow%20duck%20plush%20toy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6577559d0ec98e92f74e373d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20seven%20popular%20dog%20subscription%20boxes%20that%20included%20both%20toys%20and%20treats.%20While%20a%20few%20brands%20sent%20us%20more%20than%20one%20box%2C%20we%20evaluated%20only%20one%20box%20from%20each%20service%20for%20this%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuality%20and%20durability%20of%20toys%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBefore%20handing%20the%20toys%20over%20to%20our%2050-pound%20super%20chewer%2C%20Lyla%2C%20we%20tested%20each%20one's%20durability%20with%20a%20fork%20to%20see%20how%20it%20would%20likely%20stand%20up%20to%20a%20smaller%20dog%20who%20chews%20less%20intensely.%20We%20also%20timed%20how%20long%20it%20took%20Lyla%20to%20destroy%20the%20toys.%20Since%20she%20chews%20so%20aggressively%2C%20boxes%20with%20toys%20that%20lasted%20a%20few%20days%20scored%20highly.%20Toys%20also%20scored%20points%20for%20tough%20materials%20like%20nylon%20mesh%2C%20which%20is%20longer-lasting%20than%20polyester%20fabric.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EToy%20safety%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20avoid%20exceptionally%20hard%20toys%20or%20items%20filled%20with%20small%20bits%20of%20plastic%20that%20can%20pose%20a%20choking%20hazard.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20we%20gave%20extra%20points%20to%20toys%20we%20could%20indent%20with%20a%20fingernail%20and%20ones%20filled%20with%20soft%20stuffing%20instead%20of%20crinkle%20material.%20In%20our%20reviews%2C%20we've%20disclosed%20whether%20any%20toys%20didn't%20meet%20these%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuality%20and%20safety%20of%20treats%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETreats%20with%20transparent%20nutrition%20and%20ingredient%20information%20scored%20highly%2C%20while%20treats%20with%20little%20to%20no%20information%20did%20not%20perform%20well%20in%20our%20evaluation.%20While%20we%20also%20considered%20our%20tester%20dog's%20treat%20preferences%2C%20we%20gave%20more%20weight%20to%20the%20clear%20nutrition%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVariety%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20boxes%20we%20recommend%20include%20something%20for%20every%20dog.%20Boxes%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20toys%2C%20such%20as%20tug%20toys%2C%20balls%20or%20squeaky%20toys%2C%20and%20puzzle%20or%20treat-dispensing%20toys%2C%20scored%20well%20in%20our%20testing.%20We%20also%20evaluated%20treat%20variety.%20Because%20most%20boxes%20contained%20a%20similar%20mix%20of%20biscuits%20and%20small%20meaty%20bites%2C%20treats%20factored%20into%20our%20evaluation%20less.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20compared%20each%20box's%20contents%20to%20similar%20products%20sold%20at%20large%20pet%20retailers.%20We%20compared%20the%20per-box%20price%20points%20of%20single%2C%20six-month%2C%20and%2012-month%20subscription%20plans%20to%20a%20month%20of%20toy%20and%20treat%20purchases%20at%20the%20retailers.%20We%20also%20noted%20how%20long%20these%20toys%20and%20treats%20lasted%20compared%20to%20what%20we%20usually%20buy%20for%20our%20dog.%20Boxes%20that%20didn't%20offer%20better%20value%20were%20scored%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPackaging%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20deducted%20points%20for%20boxes%20with%20excessive%20packaging.%20This%20included%20individually%20wrapped%20toys%20and%20treats%2C%20oversized%20plastic%20product%20tags%2C%20and%20filling%20such%20as%20tissue%20paper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGiving%20back%20and%20sustainability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20sought%20out%20boxes%20with%20verifiable%20ties%20to%20shelters%20or%20sustainability%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheme%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%20themed%20boxes%2C%20we%20evaluated%20whether%20the%20theme%20was%20cohesive%20among%20the%20toys%20and%20treats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDog%20subscription%20box%20FAQs%3Ch3%3EAre%20dog%20box%20subscriptions%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20depends.%20One%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20subscription%20boxes%20could%20be%20a%20perfect%20fit%20for%20your%20pup%2C%20depending%20on%20their%20preferences%2C%20but%20because%20most%20boxes%20are%20pre-built%2C%20it%20might%20be%20hard%20to%20get%20exactly%20what%20your%20dog%20likes.%20If%20you%20shop%20for%20toys%20and%20treats%20yourself%2C%20you%20may%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20find%20toys%20they%20love%20rather%20than%20gambling%20on%20a%20box.%20However%2C%20the%20subscription%20boxes%20we%20tested%20were%20all%20solid%20options%2C%20and%20our%20tester%20dog%20enjoyed%20all%20the%20treats%20and%20toys%20in%20her%20boxes.%20For%20us%2C%20these%20boxes%20are%20more%20than%20worth%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EWhich%20dog%20subscription%20is%20the%20best%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20dog%20subscription%20box%20contains%20interactive%2C%20safe%20toys%20that%20encourage%20you%20to%20play%20with%20your%20pup.%20These%20toys