mar%20Verma%20on%20Friday%20shared%20a%20terrifying%20moment%20when%20Khalistani%20'goons'%20came%20very%20close%20to%20bodily%20harm%20him%20and%20attacked%20him%20with%20a%20'sharp%20object'%20-%20most%20likely%20a%20'kirpan'%20-%20in%20Alberta%20that%20could%20potentially%20harm%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20podcast%20with%20ANI%2C%20Sanjay%20Verma%20shared%20his%20experience%20of%20threats%20and%20intimidation%20from%20the%20Khalistanis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Verma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20these%20attempts%20to%20harm%20me%20bodily%2C%20that%20was%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20(RCMP)%20and%20the%20local%20police%20and%20the%20local%20police%20on%20the%20ground%20took%20immediate%20action%2C%20pushed%20him%20away%20because%20there%20was%20a%20sharp%20weapon%20and%20the%20RCMP%20then%20whisked%20me%20from%20the%20side%20door%20to%20the%20venue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20in%20Alberta.%20I%20am%20not%20an%20expert%20on%20Canadian%20law%20about%20open%20carrying%20so%20I%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20say%20that.%20But%20most%20likely%20they%20would%20have%20said%20that%20it%20was%20'kirpan'%20which%20is%20a%20small%20blade%20whereas%20they%20had%20swords%20in%20their%20hand.%20They%20could%20come%20very%2C%20very%20close%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Verma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20the%20incident%20was%20reported%2C%20Sanjay%20Verma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20all%20reported%20and%20we%20were%20told%20that%20investigations%20are%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20intimidation%20from%20the%20Khalistanis%2C%20Sanjay%20Verma%20said%20that%20the%20intimidation%20came%20through%20banned%20organisations%20associated%20with%20the%20Khalistani%20extremists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20came%20through%20emails%20during%20the%20so-called%20protests%2C%20which%20I%20call%20hooliganism%20when%20they%20gathered%20in%20front%20of%20the%20two%20consulates%20or%20the%20High%20Commission.%20They%20would%20shout%20slogans%20to%20intimidate%20us.%20Whenever%20we%20were%20attending%20public%20events%2C%20again%2C%20they%20would%20shout%20slogans%20to%20intimidate%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20an%20incident%2C%20Sanjay%20Verma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20one%20instance%2C%20close%20to%20Diwali%2C%20they%20created%2010%20heads%20for%20me%2C%20called%20me%20Ravan.%20And%20then%20my%20effigy%20was%20burnt%20as%20Ravan.%20Is%20that%20not%20hate%20speech%3F%20Then%20they%20created%20another%20poster%20of%20mine.%20And%20they%20riddled%20it%20with%20bullets.%20Is%20that%20not%20hate%20speech%3F%20Then%20what%20is%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20reported%20this%20to%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%20The%20response%20was%20that%20we%20forwarded%20it%20to%20the%20relevant%20authorities%2C%20which%20is%20correct.%20We%20also%20do%20the%20same.%20But%20the%20report%20never%20came%20back.%20Okay.%20So%20we%20presume%20that%20nothing%20happened.%20So%20we%20presume%20that%20it%20went%20into%20a%20black%20box.%20Not%20to%20come%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%2C%20at%20any%20point%2C%20felt%20threatened%20physically%2C%C2%A0Sanjay%20Verma%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThreatened%2C%20yes.%20But%20did%20I%20become%20threatened%3F%20No.%20In%20most%20of%20my%20public%20events%2C%20there%20will%20be%20these%20hooligans%20outside%20shouting%20slogans%20against%20India%2C%20but%20also%20against%20me.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20very%20burly-looking%20tall%20guys%20who%20would%20also%20gesture%20to%20physically%20harm%20me%2C%20but%20just%20the%20gestures%2C%20except%20for%20a%20few%20incidents.%20And%20so%20they%20tried.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20came%20close%20to%20me.%20They%20tried%20to%20intimidate%20me%20through%20such%2C%20slogans%20shouting%2C%20and%20abusing%20me%20verbally.%20That%20was%20reported%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20his%20security%2C%20Sanjay%20Verma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20Canadian%20security%2C%20both%20federal%20and%20local.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20whether%20he%2C%20at%20any%20time%2C%20doubted%20their%20ability%20to%20protect%20him%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20that%20I%20won't%20say.%20They%20were%20very%20professional%2C%20well-trained%2C%20and%20very%20respectful.%20So%20as%20far%20as%20the%20police%20officers%20who%20were%20protecting%20us%20and%20now%20protecting%20my%20colleagues%20there%2C%20very%2C%20very%20professional%2C%20never%20had%20an%20iota%20of%20doubt%20on%20their%20professionalism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20statement%20which%20we%20saw%20in%20the%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20press%20briefing%2C%20where%20even%20the%20investigation%20has%20not%20been%20concluded%2C%20that%20was%20a%20sad%20thing%20to%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Verma%20said%20that%20he%20was%20there%20to%20serve%20India's%20national%20interest%20and%20was%20committed%20to%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20diplomacy%20for%20most%20of%20us%20would%20be%2C%20you%20know%2C%20being%20nice%2C%20nice%20cities.%20But%20then%20the%20final%20objective%20of%20diplomacy%20happens%20to%20be%20to%20safeguard%20your%20national%20interest.%20National%20interest%20could%20be%20improving%20relationships.%20National%20interest%20could%20be%20raising%20awareness%20against%20these%20Khalistani%20goons.%20All%20these%20are%20national%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we%20work%20for%20the%20national%20interests.%20It%20so%20happened%20that%20my%20national%20interest%20was%20a%20bit%20different%20than%20the%20national%20interest%20of%20most%20other%20ambassadors%20in%20other%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sanjay%20Verma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Verma%20was%20recalled%20from%20Canada%20after%