Url%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Exclusive%3A%201st%20Images%20Of%20Chinese%20Troops'%20Disengagement%20In%20Ladakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20India%20announced%20that%20a%20patrolling%20arrangement%20had%20been%20reached%20with%20China%2C%20NDTV%20has%20accessed%20the%20first%20satellite%20images%20of%20disengagement%20taking%20place%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20was%20announced%20on%20Monday%20and%20a%20satellite%20image%20from%20the%20Depsang%20plains%20taken%20on%20October%2011%20shows%20four%20vehicles%20and%20two%20tents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20image%20taken%20on%20Friday%20shows%20that%20the%20tents%20have%20been%20removed%20and%20the%20vehicles%20are%20moving%20away.%20The%20land%20on%20which%20the%20tents%20stood%20has%20also%20been%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-resolution%20images%20have%20been%20provided%20by%20Maxar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fjvt800h_depsang-disengagement_625x300_25_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20images%20from%20Depsang%20are%20from%20near%20the%20'Y%20Junction'%20from%20where%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20prevented%20from%20travelling%20east%20to%20India's%20patrolling%20points.%20The%20patrolling%20points%2C%20or%20PPs%2C%20mark%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20that%20India%20claims%20in%20these%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20similar%20satellite%20image%20from%20Demchok%20from%20October%209%2C%20semi-permanent%20Chinese%20structures%20can%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fi61b6l0g_demchok-disengagement_625x300_25_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20structures%20are%20missing%20in%20an%20image%20from%20the%20disputed%20site%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-china-to-complete-disengagement-process-by-end-of-this-month-sources-6871293%5C%22%3EArmy%20sources%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20that%20the%20process%20of%20disengagement%20would%20be%20completed%20in%20the%20two%20contentious%20areas%20by%20Tuesday%2C%20October%2029%2C%20%C2%A0and%20the%20troops%20would%20return%20to%20the%20positions%20that%20existed%20before%20the%20stand-off%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20began%20in%202020.%20The%20process%20includes%20the%20dismantling%20of%20structures%20and%20restoring%20the%20land%20on%20which%20they%20stood%20to%20their%20original%20condition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20both%20India%20and%20China%20will%20continue%20to%20have%20surveillance%20options%20in%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%2C%20and%20troops%20will%20inform%20the%20other%20side%20before%20stepping%20out%20on%20patrol%20%26quot%3Bto%20avoid%20any%20miscommunication%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stand-off%20began%20in%20May%202020%20and%20a%20clash%20took%20place%20in%20Ladakh's%20Galwan%20the%20next%20month%20in%20which%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20action%20and%20the%20Chinese%20side%20also%20suffered%20losses%2C%20with%20the%20exact%20number%20remaining%20unconfirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20troop%20buildup%20followed%20on%20both%20sides%20and%20military-level%20talks%20began%20taking%20place%20to%20resolve%20the%20stand-off.%20In%20September%202022%2C%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20withdrew%20from%20the%20contentious%20Gogra-Hot%20Springs%20area%20in%20Ladakh%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20pre-April-2020%20position.%3C%2Fp