6ssl%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D372572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Alia%20Bhatt%E2%80%99s%20sustainable%20style%20and%20Shalini%20Passi%E2%80%99s%20glamorous%20life%20dominate%20headlines%2C%20inspiring%20stories%20often%20go%20unnoticed.%20A%20Kerala%20couple%20planted%2010%2C000%20saplings%20during%20their%20travels%2C%20and%20a%20Manipur%20teacher%20offers%20innovative%20education%20to%20600%2B%20underprivileged%20students%20%E2%80%94%20showing%20that%20real%20change%20often%20lies%20beyond%20the%20viral%20buzz.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TBI%20Team%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BYou%20Need%20To%20Score%26quot%3B%3A%20Rohit%20SAnd%20Co.%20Delivered%20Strong%20Message%20By%20Management%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20batters'%20constant%20failure%20in%20making%20runs%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20is%20costing%20the%20team%20dear%2C%20admitted%20bowling%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Morne%20Morkel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F875-morne-morkel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMorne%20Morkel%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20as%20India%20are%20in%20danger%20of%20losing%20the%20first%20Test%20series%20at%20home%20since%202012-13.%20After%20getting%20bundled%20out%20for%20an%20abysmal%2046%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20of%20the%20opening%20Test%2C%20India%20were%20skittled%20out%20for%20a%20mere%20156%20in%20the%20first%20essay%20of%20second%20Test%20in%20Pune%20on%20Friday%20as%20New%20Zealand%20took%20firm%20control%20of%20the%20match.%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20like%20to%20have%20a%20punch%20up%20between%20batters%20and%20bowlers%20but%2C%20in%20Test%20match%20cricket%20you%20need%20to%20score%20the%20first%20innings%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20Morkel%20told%20the%20media%20during%20the%20post-day%20press%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20put%20our%20hand%20up%2C%20we%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20do%20that.%20There%20are%20world%20class%20players%20in%20our%20batting%20line%20up.%20I%20know%20that%20individually%2C%20they've%20got%20their%20processes%20and%20they%20know%20how%20to%20go%20about%20those%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorkel%20hoped%20to%20see%20a%20better%20outing%20from%20Indian%20batters%20in%20the%20second%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHopefully%2C%20we%20can%20iron%20those%20mistakes%20out%20because%20it's%20costing%20us%20at%20the%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20not%20getting%20the%20runs%20on%20the%20board%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I'm%20pretty%20sure%20there's%20enough%20experience%2C%20enough%20knowledge%20amongst%20them%20to%20rectify%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20back%20the%20team%20(to%20come%20up)%20with%20a%20strong%20response%20in%20our%20second%20innings.%20I'm%20excited%20to%20see%20how%20they%20bounce%20back%20and%20how%20they%20play%20this%20situation%20and%20the%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorkel%20said%20India%20will%20have%20to%20maintain%20belief%20and%20back%20their%20knowledge%20of%20the%20conditions%20to%20avert%20losing%20the%20match%20and%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20believe.%20This%20game%20is%20a%20funny%20game.%20Our%20guys%20are%20attacking%20players%2C%20there's%20guys%20that%20know%20these%20conditions%20well.%20Our%20talk%20before%20this%20game%20was%20that%20we%20are%20masters%20in%20these%20conditions%2C%20we%20know%20how%20to%20sum%20these%20conditions%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet's%20be%20honest%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20tough%20task.%20But%20what%20an%20opportunity%20for%20somebody%20to%20really%20inspire%20and%20put%20in%20a%20fighting%20and%20a%20top%20performance%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20way%20I%20see%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20conditions%20are%20tricky%20and%20tough%20you'll%20see%20real%20people%20stand%20up%20and%20fight%20and%20if%20we%20show%20that%20fight%20and%20somebody%20gets%20the%20momentum%20going%20in%20these%20conditions%2C%20you%20never%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorkel%20said%20the%20hosts%20wanted%20to%20see%20off%20the%20overs%20on%20Day%20One%20when%20they%20reached%2016%2F1%20in%2011%20overs%20and%20then%20find%20momentum%20on%20Day%20Two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20they%20(New%20Zealand)%20bowled%20very%20well%20in%20partnership.%20Watching%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20it%20was%20very%20hard%20for%20us%20to%20rotate%20strike%2C%20to%20keep%20the%20scoreboard%20ticking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20these%20sort%20of%20conditions%20where%20the%20ball%20is%20turning%20and%20asking%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pace%20that%20(Mitchell)%20Santner%20bowled%20today%20in%20particular%2C%20was%20spot%20on%20for%20this%20surface.%20On%20Day%20Two%2C%20arriving%20here%20this%20morning%20being%20one%20down%2C%20our%20camp%20was%20very%20confident%20that%20we%20were%20going%20to%20bat%20big%20but%20unfortunately%20we%20just%20couldn't%20get%20that%20momentum%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorkel%20praised%20New%20Zealand%20for%20coming%20to%20this%20tour%20well-prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20must%20give%20credit%20to%20New%20Zealand.%20The%20way%20they've%20adapted%20to%20conditions%2C%20the%20way%20they've%20sort%20of%20blocked%20out%20what%20is%20in%20front%20of%20them%20and%20just%20played%20the%20game%2C%20it's%20been%20incredible%20so%20far%20in%20this%20series%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDefinitely%20in%20Bangalore%20and%20here%2C%20playing%20those%20sessions%2C%20playing%20those%20important%20moments%20they've%20done%20it%20better%20than%20us%20at%20the%20moment.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20they're%20on%20top%20of%2