20them%20due%20to%20misconceptions%20and%20lack%20of%20awareness.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20that%20there%20were%20incidences%20when%20children%20took%20IFA%20tablets%20and%20they%20fainted.%20Of%20course%2C%20their%20parents%20got%20worried%20and%20were%20suspicious%20of%20the%20free%20tablets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20speaking%20to%20a%20few%20health%20providers%2C%20I%20learnt%20that%20these%20tablets%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20on%20an%20empty%20stomach.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20underprivileged%20households%2C%20breakfast%20is%20not%20a%20common%20practice%2C%20so%20most%20children%20rely%20on%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20provided%20at%20school.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20given%20Iron%20and%20Folic%20acid%20tablets%20during%20morning%20prayers%2C%20which%20put%20them%20at%20risk%20of%20fainting%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20food%20beforehand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20he%20introduced%20changes%20to%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20programme%2C%20adding%20iron-rich%20foods%20and%20folic%20acid%20tablets%20to%20the%20diet%2C%20and%20educating%20parents%20and%20students%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20taking%20IFA%20tablets%20after%20meals%20to%20avoid%20adverse%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20smooth%20implementation%2C%20teams%20were%20formed%20at%20block%20and%20district%20levels%20to%20monitor%20the%20distribution%20and%20consumption%20of%20these%20tablets%2C%20with%20regular%20reports%20sent%20to%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office%20every%2015%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20also%20established%20kitchen%20gardens%20in%20nearly%20756%20public%20and%20private%20scho