.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20ensures%20that%20the%20nutritional%20content%20of%20the%20leaves%20remains%20in%20the%20final%20product%20for%20distribution.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-17-1729263081.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371318%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20ensures%20that%20the%20nutritional%20content%20of%20the%20leaves%20remains%20in%20the%20final%20product%20for%20distribution.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20the%20nutritional%20value%20of%20moringa%20leaves%2C%20Jitender%20and%20Sarla%20invested%20in%20a%20state-of-the-art%20drying%20setup%20that%20ensures%20optimal%20drying%20conditions%20while%20retaining%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20beneficial%20properties.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20plucking%20stems%20with%20leaves%2C%20we%20wash%20them%20twice%20and%20bundle%20seven%20to%20nine%20stems%20together%20so%20that%20each%20leaf%20is%20separated%20for%20easier%20drying%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarla%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20dry%20the%20leaves%20under%20large%20fans%20and%20also%20in%20a%20controlled%20greenhouse%20setup%2C%20where%20energy%20gets%20trapped%20and%20the%20temperature%20is%208-10%20degrees%20hotter%20than%20outside.%20After%2012%20hours%2C%20the%20leaves%20become%20crunchy%20and%20we%20separate%20them%20from%20the%20stems.%20We%20then%20make%20a%20coarse%20powder%20in%20a%20pulveriser%20and%20remove%20stalks%20before%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20meticulous%20process%2C%20Jitender%20says%2C%20ensures%20that%20the%20nutritional%20content%20of%20the%20leaves%20remains%20in%20the%20final%20product%20for%20distribution.%20%E2%80%9CMoringa%20is%20a%20summer-loving%20plant%20in%20North%20India.%20We%20harvest%20leaves%20for%20about%20seven%20months%20between%20April%20and%20October%2C%20with%20the%20plant%20remaining%20dormant%20for%20the%20remaining%20five%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jitender%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarla%20points%20out%20that%20to%20ensure%20high-quality%20crop%20production%2C%20they%20adopted%20a%20jungle%20farming%20method.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20method%2C%20we%20do%20not%20till%20the%20soil%20and%20use%20weeds%20and%20other%20leaves%20as%20mulch.%20We%20also%20avoid%20harmful%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20pesticides%2C%20and%20weedicides.%20This%20ensures%20that%20our%20soil%20has%20good%20aeration%20and%20high%20carbon%20content.%20You%20can%20only%20produce%20good-quality%20moringa%20leaves%20if%20your%20soil%20is%20fertile%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20to%20becoming%20a%20profitable%20venture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarla%20informs%20that%20about%201%2C000%20kg%20of%20dry%20powder%20can%20be%20produced%20from%20one%20acre%20of%20land.%20By%20selling%20a%20200-gram%20packet%20of%20moringa%20powder%2C%20the%20couple%20earns%20Rs%20650.%20On%20average%2C%20they%20make%20sales%20of%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20per%20month%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20per%20acre%20every%20season.%20They%20established%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20metro%20cities%20like%20Delhi%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Gurugram%20primarily%20through%20word%20of%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20with%20two%20acres%20for%20cultivating%20moringa%20powder%2C%20but%20our%20demand%20is%20growing%20at%20twice%20the%20rate%20of%20our%20production.%20Next%20year%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20expand%20our%20moringa%20fields%20from%20four%20to%20eight%20acres%20and%20explore%20international%20markets%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jitender%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20employs%20many%20rural%20women%20to%20pluck%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20package%20moringa%20leaves%20powder.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-18-1729263150.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371319%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20employs%20many%20rural%20women%20to%20pluck%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20package%20moringa%20leaves%20powder.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20the%20shift%20from%20a%20corporate%20career%20to%20farming%20has%20not%20only%20been%20professionally%20rewarding%20but%20has%20also%20transformed%20his%20personal%20health%20and%20well-being.%20Free%20from%20the%20joint%20pains%20and%20high%20blood%20pressure%20that%20once%20plagued%20his%20urban%20lifestyle%2C%20Jitender%20now%20embraces%20a%20vibrant%20and%20active%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20sending%20the%20powder%20for%20packaging%2C%20we%20keep%20a%20few%20jars%20aside%20for%20ourselves.%20Personally%2C%20daily%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367162%2Fscientist-quits-job-at-tamil-nadu-agriculture-university-to-become-farmer-sells-value-added-moringa-products-worldwide%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumption%20of%20moringa%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20replaced%20my%20need%20for%20conventional%20medications.%20I%20no%20longer%20have%20any%20health%20issues.%20My%20blood%20pressure%20now%20remains%20between%20120%20and%20130%2C%20and%20I%20can%20do%20five%20chin-ups%20at%20once%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20moving%20to%20my%20village%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20decisions%20we%20ever%20made.%20Working%20in%20the%20fields%2C%20we%20are%20living%20a%20luxurious%20lifestyle%20in%20our%20village%2C%20with%20city%20amenities%20nearby%20and%20pollution%20far%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Sarla%20Mann%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC9916933%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoringa%20oleifera%3A%20An%20Updated%20Comprehensive%20Review%20of%20Its%20Pharmacological%20Activities%2C%20Ethnomedicinal%2C%20Phytopharmaceutical%20Formulation%2C%20Clinical%2C%20Phytochemical%2C%20and%20Toxicological%20Aspects%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20in%20PubMed%20Central%20(PMC)%20in%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729608103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26ssl%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D371313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20working%20for%2011%20years%20at%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20(TCS)%2C%20Jitender%20Mann%20moved%20back%20to%20his%20ancestral%20home%20in%20Haryana%20to%20embrace%20organic%20farming.%20Along%20with%20his%20wife%20Sarla%2C%20he%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20to%20promote%20the%20goodness%20of%20moringa%20and%20developed%20a%20profitable%20venture%20out%20of%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A56%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F371313%2Fcouple-quit-city-life-to-move-to-haryana-village-earns-lakhs-with-moringa-farming%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vikas%20Khanna%20on%20How%20Indian%20Heritage%20and%20Street%20Food%20Inspire%20His%20Culinary%20Journey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20last%20day%20of%20Navratri%2C%20the%20Hindu%20festival%20celebrated%20with%20great%20pomp%20and%20splendour%20over%20nine%20nights.%20The%20fireworks%20outside%20my%20window%20oblige%20with%20drumrolls%20for%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20an%20evening%20I%20will%20remember%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20few%20seconds%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359321%2Fvikas-khanna-chef-journey-success-story-masterchef-michelin-star-bungalow-restaurant-new-york-amritsar-india-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVikas%20Khanna%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20internet%E2%80%99s%20beloved%20chef%20%E2%80%94%20takes%20a%20few%20seconds%20to%20unmute%20his%20mic%20and%20adjust%20his%20camera%2C%20giving%20me%20a%20clear%20view%20of%20him%20in%20his%20elegant%20New%20York%20City%20home%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20smile%20at%20this%20%E2%80%98pinch-me%E2%80%99%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20from%20the%20outset%2C%20Khanna%20is%20chipper%3B%20no%20one%20(except%20probably%20the%20general%20manager%20at%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%2C%20Sameer%20Bhatt)%20would%20guess%20he%20has%20pulled%20an%20all-nighter.%20Well%20into%20the%20wee%20hours%20of%20the%20morning%2C%20Khanna%20was%20attempting%20to%20replicate%20the%20intricate%20wings%20of%20a%20peacock%E2%80%99s%20feathers%20onto%20the%20surface%20of%20a%20piece%20of%20coconut%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Indian%20sweet).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20decades%20of%20culinary%20experience%20ensured%20he%20aced%20the%20task.%20And%20now%20for%20replicating%20the%20same%20onto%20a%20hundred-odd%20pieces!%20Known%20to%20push%20the%20envelope%2C%20Khanna%20does%20justice%20to%20this%20reputation%20when%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20each%20feather%20to%20be%20exactly%20alike.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20how%20the%20plumage%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandirs%20%3C%2Fem%3E(temples)%20in%20Indian%20homes%2C%20Khanna%20was%20keen%20that%20every%20guest%20at%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20his%20dream%20restaurant%20project%20launched%20in%20New%20York%20in%20March%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20return%20home%20that%20day%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288997%2Fpunjabi-wrestler-harbans-vig-invented-indias-loved-dhodha-barfi-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebox%20of%20coconut%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20spot%20the%20delicate%20%3Cem%3Emor%20pankh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(peacock%20feather)%2C%20and%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1729603369.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20created%20'Bungalow'%20in%20New%20York%20as%20an%20ode%20to%20street%20vendors%20of%20India%20and%20the%20food%20he%20grew%20up%20eating%20in%20Amritsar%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1729603369.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1729603369.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024